- maintain open directory information on refresh
- map C to: change current working directory to root directory
- map c to: change current working directory to selected directory
- map K to: go to first sibling in directory
- map J to: go to last sibling in directory
- map H to: recursively close all nodes below current one
- map L to: recursively open all nodes under current one
- map q to: quit tree window
- map m to: minimize tree window
- figure out how to delete the last line in the tree buffer
- figure out how to map cmd-click to just activating the window
  instead of opening the node
- extract config options

